These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: collecting, skydiving, dancing, filmmaking
Sport: water-polo, snowboarding, volleyball, skateboarding
1. Hobby:dancing is between Sport:volleyball and Sport:snowboarding##2
2. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left or right of Sport:volleyball##3
3. Sport:volleyball is not to the left of Sport:volleyball##8
4. Sport:snowboarding != Hobby:dancing##6
5. Hobby:dancing is somewhere to the right of Hobby:collecting##5
6. Hobby:collecting is on the right of Sport:water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | collecting | dancing | skydiving  |
| Sport   | water-polo | volleyball   | skateboarding  | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: kale, asparagus, plum, garlic
Job: entrepreneur, electrician, videographer, security-guard
1. Job:security-guard is not to the left of Job:security-guard##8
2. Food:kale is somewhere to the right of Food:garlic##5
3. Food:kale == Job:electrician##1
4. Food:garlic is between Food:kale and Food:asparagus##2
5. Food:asparagus is somewhere between Food:plum and Job:entrepreneur##7
6. Job:videographer is somewhere to the left of Food:asparagus##5
7. Job:entrepreneur is not to the left of Job:entrepreneur##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | plum | asparagus          | garlic | kale     |
| Job    | videographer      | security-guard | entrepreneur | electrician |

