.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Job: fisherman, police-officer, firefighter, dancer
Movie-Genre: animation, sports, crime, western
1. Movie-Genre:animation is not to the left of Job:firefighter##8
2. Movie-Genre:sports is on the far left##1
3. Job:police-officer is on the right of Job:fisherman##1
4. Job:police-officer is in an even position##4
5. Job:dancer is on the far left or far right##3
6. Job:fisherman is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:western##5
7. Job:dancer == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | firefighter     | dancer |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | western   | animation | crime    |

