2. Sport:golf is not to the left of Sport:rugby##8
3. Sport:badminton is on the right of Music-Genre:r&b##1
4. Music-Genre:electronic is not to the right of Sport:badminton##8
5. Music-Genre:classical == Sport:golf##1
6. Music-Genre:classical is on the right of Sport:badminton##1
7. Music-Genre:soul is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:electronic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | r&b         | electronic   | classical    |
| Sport         | rugby | skiing | badminton | golf |

