Transport: bike, train, subway, van
1. Music-Genre:salsa is between Music-Genre:punk and Transport:bike##2
2. Transport:van is on the far left##1
3. Transport:van is on the left or right of Music-Genre:salsa##3
4. Music-Genre:d&b is somewhere to the right of Transport:bike##5
5. Transport:train == Transport:train##1
6. Music-Genre:blues != Transport:subway##6
7. Music-Genre:punk is not to the right of Music-Genre:blues##8
8. Transport:bike is not to the left of Transport:train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | salsa | blues | d&b |
| Transport     | van | train       | bike  | subway    |

