5. Pet:goldfish is somewhere between Transport:tram and Transport:snowmobile##7
6. Pet:goldfish is on the left of Pet:rat##1
7. Transport:bus is between Transport:helicopter and Pet:turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig    | goldfish | rat | turtle |
| Transport   | tram | helicopter      | bus     | snowmobile     |

 